<template>
    <ContentCard>
      BOTS
    </ContentCard>
  </template>
  
  
<script>
import ContentCard from "../../../components/ContentCard"
import $ from "jquery"
import { useStore } from "vuex";


export default {
    components: {
        ContentCard
    },
    setup() {
      const store = useStore();
      $.ajax({
        url: "http://localhost:8888/user/bot/add/",
        type: "POST",
        data: {
          botName: "   ",
          description: "",
          content: "code",
        },
        headers: {
          Authorization: "Bearer " + store.state.user.token
        },
        success(resp) {
          console.log(resp);
        },
        error(resp) {
          console.log(resp);
        },
      })
    }
}
</script>
